column5:
Product Description
Filled with 10oz of American Soybean WaxTM. Measures 3.25"h x 3.75"w with 45+ hour burn time.

Refilling information: One container of Candle Refill Wax will refill this container twice. You will want to use the #62 wick, and, to create the same look as the original candle, use our White Candle Refill Wax when refilling.

Occasionally we are out of a certain color/shape in the pottery, and we reserve the right to substitute color/shape of the same size and fragrance. If you are set on a specific color/shape, please give us a call toll free at 888-272-2773 M-F from 9am to 4pm EST. We can let you know exactly what we have available!

* = Best selling fragrance

column5:
Product Description

column1: NEW! Illumination Wax Warmer Square Tuscan Cream
column4: Home > Wax Warmers > Illumination Wax Warmers > NEW! Illumination Wax Warmer Square Tuscan Cream
column5:
Product Description
The Illumination Warmers are lovely tabletop warmers that plug into an outlet and use an electric bulb (25W) to fill any room with fragrance! We recommend using these with our Drizzle MeltsTM, a scoop of our Candle Refill Wax, one of our Tarts, or our Fragrance Oils. They will give the ambiance of a candle without the flame, while still releasing intense fragrance!

Measures 4.5"l x 4.5"w x 6.5"h

Use our 25Watt Warmer Replacement Bulb when replacing bulb.

We recommend using these with our Drizzle MeltsTM, a scoop of our Candle Refill Wax, one of our Tarts, or our Fragrance Oils. They will give the ambiance of a candle without the flame, while still releasing intense fragrance!

Measures 4.5"l x 4.5"w x 6.5"h

Use our 25Watt Warmer Replacement Bulb when replacing bulb.

Refilling information: One container of Candle Refill Wax will refill this container one and a half times. You will want to use two of the #51 wicks, and, to create the same look as the original candle, use our new White Candle Refill Wax when refilling.

* = Best selling fragrance
